{"tid":687802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇噚日鍵國派比港台頭條新聞撚到一楝都冇","createTime":"2018-06-02T14:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T00:25:03.000Z","uid":63846,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc908a1bb2ef37712084cfe0399dab62a934a482","tid":687802,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:31:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/M_WvJu4ms14?t=8m42s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM_WvJu4ms14%3Ft%3D8m42s&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=bd2caa71\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M_WvJu4ms14?t=8m42s</a><br />\n8m42s<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae596de984abeaf95631c62ac41aae2e3ab4775","tid":687802,"uid":48670,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:33:14.000Z","msg":"兩件五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eceb3df590e40944463b6094f0322af6d61ec32","tid":687802,"uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:35:13.000Z","msg":"人地講學生會咁講, <br />\n<br />\n係委婉講法, <br />\n<br />\n費事公開當面屌柒你支聯會囉<br />\n<br />\n難道要講到好白, 你老母支聯會食人血饅頭咩?"},{"pid":"25eadbbeba5ab0eb58a83d93e3db289edca70b42","tid":687802,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"學生會既說法, 係委婉式既講法, <br />\n<br />\n意即唔撚知你班友係維園做乜有乜意義?<br />\n<br />\n委婉說法係英國政界係好常見, 尤其法律界<br />\n<br />\n難道好似兩件頭條新聞既老野大中華膠 / 支那人咁, 唔直屌唔明咩?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/25/125751_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F125751_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=510db1fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"472656a25977d814238588a4cf9719c5b38aa11a","tid":687802,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd01f4993a3f33994d4fd5a07f8330c62d584675","tid":687802,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:26:57.000Z","msg":"大家其實, 知唔知點解維園六四晚會係食人血饅頭？<br />\n<br />\n有好多唔同團體推籌款車<br />\n<br />\n籌既款唔會交比六四北京死難者家屬 / 倖存者<br />\n<br />\n籌既款係自己袋, 並且要上繳10分1 (好似係) 比支聯會<br />\n<br />\n咁樣唔係食人血饅頭, 唔係消費北京死難者, 係撚乜野？"},{"pid":"8efb8c80cb12facbe9355a595fe87245cb199b29","tid":687802,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T17:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/012212_14842a158b5677af25672d5b6a59c0b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F012212_14842a158b5677af25672d5b6a59c0b5.jpg&h=008a27fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問支聯會建設民主中國後會否制止單程證新移民來港？到時會否以廣東話作為主要教學語言？香港係民主中國之下可以保留多少自治權力？如果以上三者答案皆否，為何香港人仲要建設民主中國？<br />\n<br />\n喂，我答左了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdcb8558ce9facede6e05097660b7b93700afca7","tid":687802,"uid":550,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T18:53:58.000Z","msg":"頭條新聞都仲睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港台出名左膠集中營啦 <br />\n吳志森曾志豪出晒名仆街左膠專咬本土派"},{"pid":"24aacc49e72fcdd1d8d4191428a093d3467c3896","tid":687802,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T19:14:08.000Z","msg":"吳志森同曾志豪一向反本土丶港獨主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31af0a967d9fece78ed62807cf96fe695400a685","tid":687802,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:25:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港成班冚家挪住外國護照既大愛支，仲要班後生燒多幾多青春，去為一個一早燈紅酒綠紙醉金迷既遠方城市哭喪自瀆？？？</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>當年中國64<br />\n如果無香港人傷亡<br />\n香港駛唔駛年年攪咁多活動悼念<br />\n全球無一個地方好似香港大陣象</blockquote>大中華膠多 個時好多都對中國有幻想有希望</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要悼念，班大愛支係咪最應該為六四後仲支持民主回西路樓死先呢？？？尤其個班之後冚家攞定護照走既！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span>"}]}